[
  {
    "speaker": "char_gong_zi_yu",
    "speaker_name": "公子羽",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "果然不愧是天下无双的高手。",
    "tone": "微笑",
    "chapter": 22,
    "line": 8
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_zhuo_fu_ren",
    "speaker_name": "卓夫人",
    "listener": "char_gong_zi_yu",
    "text": "他连动都没有动，你就能看出他是高手？",
    "tone": "疑问",
    "chapter": 22,
    "line": 12
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_gong_zi_yu",
    "speaker_name": "公子羽",
    "listener": "char_zhuo_fu_ren",
    "text": "就因为他没有动，所以才是天下无双的高手。",
    "tone": "认真",
    "chapter": 22,
    "line": 14
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_zhuo_fu_ren",
    "speaker_name": "卓夫人",
    "listener": "char_gong_zi_yu",
    "text": "难道不动比动还难？",
    "tone": "疑问",
    "chapter": 22,
    "line": 16
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_gong_zi_yu",
    "speaker_name": "公子羽",
    "listener": "char_zhuo_fu_ren",
    "text": "难得多了。",
    "tone": "认真",
    "chapter": 22,
    "line": 18
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_zhuo_fu_ren",
    "speaker_name": "卓夫人",
    "listener": "char_gong_zi_yu",
    "text": "我不懂。",
    "tone": "疑问",
    "chapter": 22,
    "line": 20
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_gong_zi_yu",
    "speaker_name": "公子羽",
    "listener": "char_zhuo_fu_ren",
    "text": "你应该懂。你若是傅红雪，若是知道我忽然到了你身后，你会怎么样？",
    "tone": "认真",
    "chapter": 22,
    "line": 22
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_zhuo_fu_ren",
    "speaker_name": "卓夫人",
    "listener": "char_gong_zi_yu",
    "text": "我一定会很吃惊！",
    "tone": "惊讶",
    "chapter": 22,
    "line": 24
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_gong_zi_yu",
    "speaker_name": "公子羽",
    "listener": "char_zhuo_fu_ren",
    "text": "吃惊难免要警戒提防，就难免要动。",
    "tone": "认真",
    "chapter": 22,
    "line": 26
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_zhuo_fu_ren",
    "speaker_name": "卓夫人",
    "listener": "char_gong_zi_yu",
    "text": "不错！",
    "tone": "肯定",
    "chapter": 22,
    "line": 28
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_gong_zi_yu",
    "speaker_name": "公子羽",
    "listener": "char_zhuo_fu_ren",
    "text": "只要你一动，你就死了！",
    "tone": "冷酷",
    "chapter": 22,
    "line": 30
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_zhuo_fu_ren",
    "speaker_name": "卓夫人",
    "listener": "char_gong_zi_yu",
    "text": "为什么？",
    "tone": "疑问",
    "chapter": 22,
    "line": 32
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_gong_zi_yu",
    "speaker_name": "公子羽",
    "listener": "char_zhuo_fu_ren",
    "text": "因为，你根本不知道我会从什么地方出手，所以无论你怎么移动，都可以造成致命的错误。",
    "tone": "冷酷",
    "chapter": 22,
    "line": 34
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_zhuo_fu_ren",
    "speaker_name": "卓夫人",
    "listener": "char_gong_zi_yu",
    "text": "像你这么样的对手若是忽然到了一个人身后，无论谁都难免会紧张的，就算人不动，背上的肌肉也难免会抽紧。",
    "tone": "认真",
    "chapter": 22,
    "line": 36
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_gong_zi_yu",
    "speaker_name": "公子羽",
    "listener": "char_zhuo_fu_ren",
    "text": "可是他没有，我虽然已在他身后站了很久，他全身上下连一点变化都没有！",
    "tone": "认真",
    "chapter": 22,
    "line": 38
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_zhuo_fu_ren",
    "speaker_name": "卓夫人",
    "listener": "char_gong_zi_yu",
    "text": "现在我总算明白了，不动的确比动难得多！",
    "tone": "恍然",
    "chapter": 22,
    "line": 40
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_zhuo_fu_ren",
    "speaker_name": "卓夫人",
    "listener": "char_gong_zi_yu",
    "text": "他不动你难道就没有机会出手？",
    "tone": "疑问",
    "chapter": 22,
    "line": 44
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_gong_zi_yu",
    "speaker_name": "公子羽",
    "listener": "char_zhuo_fu_ren",
    "text": "不动就是动，所有动作变化的终点，就是不动。",
    "tone": "认真",
    "chapter": 22,
    "line": 48
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_zhuo_fu_ren",
    "speaker_name": "卓夫人",
    "listener": "char_gong_zi_yu",
    "text": "空门太多，反而变得没有空门了，因为整个人都已变成空的，空空荡荡，虚无缥渺，所以你反而不知道应该从何处出手？",
    "tone": "认真",
    "chapter": 22,
    "line": 50
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_gong_zi_yu",
    "speaker_name": "公子羽",
    "listener": "char_zhuo_fu_ren",
    "text": "这道理我就知道你一定会懂的。",
    "tone": "微笑",
    "chapter": 22,
    "line": 52
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_zhuo_fu_ren",
    "speaker_name": "卓夫人",
    "listener": "char_gong_zi_yu",
    "text": "我也知道你根本就不会出手。你若要在背后杀他，有很多次机会都比这次好得多。",
    "tone": "平静",
    "chapter": 22,
    "line": 54
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_zhuo_fu_ren",
    "speaker_name": "卓夫人",
    "listener": "char_gong_zi_yu",
    "text": "因为你的目的并不是要杀他，而是要击败他。",
    "tone": "平静",
    "chapter": 22,
    "line": 58
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_gong_zi_yu",
    "speaker_name": "公子羽",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "要杀他容易，要击败他就难得多了。",
    "tone": "无奈",
    "chapter": 22,
    "line": 60
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
    "listener": "char_gong_zi_yu",
    "text": "你为什么要舍易而求难？",
    "tone": "疑问",
    "chapter": 22,
    "line": 66
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_gong_zi_yu",
    "speaker_name": "公子羽",
    "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "text": "因为你是傅红雪，我是公子羽。",
    "tone": "深沉",
    "chapter": 22,
    "line": 68
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
    "listener": "char_gong_zi_yu",
    "text": "想不到公子羽竟不敢以真面目见人。",
    "tone": "冷笑",
    "chapter": 22,
    "line": 74
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_zhuo_fu_ren",
    "speaker_name": "卓夫人",
    "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "text": "你又错了。",
    "tone": "平静",
    "chapter": 22,
    "line": 76
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_zhuo_fu_ren",
    "speaker_name": "卓夫人",
    "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "text": "你现在看见的，就是公子羽的真面目。",
    "tone": "认真",
    "chapter": 22,
    "line": 80
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
    "listener": "char_zhuo_fu_ren",
    "text": "我看见的只不过是个面具。",
    "tone": "冷酷",
    "chapter": 22,
    "line": 82
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_zhuo_fu_ren",
    "speaker_name": "卓夫人",
    "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "text": "我脸上难道没有戴面具？难道你一生下来就是这种冰冰冷冷连一点血色都没有的样子？难道这不是你的真面目！",
    "tone": "激动",
    "chapter": 22,
    "line": 84
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_zhuo_fu_ren",
    "speaker_name": "卓夫人",
    "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "text": "其实你应该明白的，无论他长的是什么样子都不重要，只要你知道他是公子羽，这一点才是最重要的。",
    "tone": "认真",
    "chapter": 22,
    "line": 88
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_gong_zi_yu",
    "speaker_name": "公子羽",
    "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "text": "我并不想看你的真面目，我只要知道你是傅红雪，就已够了。",
    "tone": "淡然",
    "chapter": 22,
    "line": 94
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
    "listener": "char_gong_zi_yu",
    "text": "现在你已知道我是傅红雪，我已知道你是公子羽。",
    "tone": "认真",
    "chapter": 22,
    "line": 96
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_gong_zi_yu",
    "speaker_name": "公子羽",
    "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "text": "所以有件事我们现在一定要解决。",
    "tone": "认真",
    "chapter": 22,
    "line": 98
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
    "listener": "char_gong_zi_yu",
    "text": "什么事？",
    "tone": "疑问",
    "chapter": 22,
    "line": 100
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_gong_zi_yu",
    "speaker_name": "公子羽",
    "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "text": "我们两个人之中，现在已只有一个人能活下去。",
    "tone": "冷酷",
    "chapter": 22,
    "line": 102
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_gong_zi_yu",
    "speaker_name": "公子羽",
    "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "text": "谁强，谁就活下去。",
    "tone": "冷酷",
    "chapter": 22,
    "line": 104
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
    "listener": "char_gong_zi_yu",
    "text": "这种事好像只有一种方法解决！",
    "tone": "认真",
    "chapter": 22,
    "line": 106
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_gong_zi_yu",
    "speaker_name": "公子羽",
    "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "text": "不错，只有一种法子。自古以来，就只有这一种法子。",
    "tone": "认真",
    "chapter": 22,
    "line": 108
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_gong_zi_yu",
    "speaker_name": "公子羽",
    "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "text": "所以我一定要亲手击败你。",
    "tone": "冷酷",
    "chapter": 22,
    "line": 110
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
    "listener": "char_gong_zi_yu",
    "text": "否则你就情愿死？",
    "tone": "疑问",
    "chapter": 22,
    "line": 112
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_gong_zi_yu",
    "speaker_name": "公子羽",
    "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "text": "否则我就非死不可。",
    "tone": "悲伤",
    "chapter": 22,
    "line": 114
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
    "listener": "char_gong_zi_yu",
    "text": "我不懂。",
    "tone": "疑问",
    "chapter": 22,
    "line": 116
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_gong_zi_yu",
    "speaker_name": "公子羽",
    "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "text": "你应该懂的。我不要别人杀你，就为了要证明我比你强。我一定要做天下最强的人，否则我宁可死。",
    "tone": "认真",
    "chapter": 22,
    "line": 118
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_gong_zi_yu",
    "speaker_name": "公子羽",
    "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "text": "武林就像是个独立的王国，只能允许一个帝王存在，不是我，就是你！",
    "tone": "讥诮",
    "chapter": 22,
    "line": 120
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
    "listener": "char_gong_zi_yu",
    "text": "这次只怕是你错了！",
    "tone": "冷酷",
    "chapter": 22,
    "line": 122
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_gong_zi_yu",
    "speaker_name": "公子羽",
    "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "text": "我没有错。有很多事都能证明，除了我之外，你就是当今天下武功最强的人！",
    "tone": "认真",
    "chapter": 22,
    "line": 124
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_gong_zi_yu",
    "speaker_name": "公子羽",
    "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "text": "你能活着走进这屋子，并不是件容易事，不是运气。",
    "tone": "认真",
    "chapter": 22,
    "line": 128
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_zhuo_fu_ren",
    "speaker_name": "卓夫人",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "决不是。",
    "tone": "认真",
    "chapter": 22,
    "line": 130
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_gong_zi_yu",
    "speaker_name": "公子羽",
    "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "text": "你应该记得，这是凤凰集。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 22,
    "line": 142
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_gong_zi_yu",
    "speaker_name": "公子羽",
    "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "text": "这一战你击败了燕南飞。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 22,
    "line": 146
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_gong_zi_yu",
    "speaker_name": "公子羽",
    "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "text": "这一战你击败了五行双杀。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 22,
    "line": 150
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_gong_zi_yu",
    "speaker_name": "公子羽",
    "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "text": "杜雷本是江湖少见的好手，他的刀法是从苦难中磨练出来的，虽然有些骄矜做作，我还是想不到你—刀就能杀了他！",
    "tone": "叹息",
    "chapter": 22,
    "line": 156
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
    "listener": "char_gong_zi_yu",
    "text": "杀人的刀法，本就只有一刀！",
    "tone": "冷酷",
    "chapter": 22,
    "line": 158
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_gong_zi_yu",
    "speaker_name": "公子羽",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "不念，念动神知，后发先至，以不变应万变，一刀的确就已够了！",
    "tone": "叹息",
    "chapter": 22,
    "line": 160
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_zhuo_fu_ren",
    "speaker_name": "卓夫人",
    "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "text": "让我最想不到的是，你居然能从孔雀山庄那地室中逃出来！",
    "tone": "惊讶",
    "chapter": 22,
    "line": 166
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_zhuo_fu_ren",
    "speaker_name": "卓夫人",
    "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "text": "她是根绳子，我们本想用她来绑住你的手，你心里若是一直惦记着她和那两个孩子，你的手就等于被绑住了。",
    "tone": "认真",
    "chapter": 22,
    "line": 172
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_zhuo_fu_ren",
    "speaker_name": "卓夫人",
    "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "text": "但是我们却想不到，在那种情况下，你居然还能杀了天王斩鬼刀！",
    "tone": "惊讶",
    "chapter": 22,
    "line": 178
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
    "listener": "char_zhuo_fu_ren",
    "text": "那时你们已准备让她暴露身份，为什么还要她杀杜十七？",
    "tone": "愤怒",
    "chapter": 22,
    "line": 180
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_zhuo_fu_ren",
    "speaker_name": "卓夫人",
    "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "text": "因为我们还要利用她做最后一件事。",
    "tone": "平静",
    "chapter": 22,
    "line": 182
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
    "listener": "char_zhuo_fu_ren",
    "text": "你们要她用那两个孩子逼我拿出天地交征阴阳大悲赋？",
    "tone": "冷酷",
    "chapter": 22,
    "line": 184
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_zhuo_fu_ren",
    "speaker_name": "卓夫人",
    "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "text": "直到那时候我们才相信，《阴阳大悲赋》并没有落在你手里，因为我们知道你为了那两个孩子，是不惜栖牲一切的。",
    "tone": "认真",
    "chapter": 22,
    "line": 186
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_zhuo_fu_ren",
    "speaker_name": "卓夫人",
    "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "text": "只可惜你居然练成了大移穴法，居然没有死在她手里，更可惜的是，你居然狠不下心来杀她！",
    "tone": "无奈",
    "chapter": 22,
    "line": 188
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_zhuo_fu_ren",
    "speaker_name": "卓夫人",
    "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "text": "那时我们本来以为你已完了，就算你还能杀人，也只不过是个疯狂的刽子手，已不值得公子对付你。",
    "tone": "平静",
    "chapter": 22,
    "line": 194
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_zhuo_fu_ren",
    "speaker_name": "卓夫人",
    "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "text": "如果你已不是武林中最强的人，就算死在阴沟里，我们也不会开心的，所以那时我们已准备找别人去杀你了。",
    "tone": "平静",
    "chapter": 22,
    "line": 198
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
    "listener": "char_zhuo_fu_ren",
    "text": "只可惜能杀我的人也不多。",
    "tone": "冷酷",
    "chapter": 22,
    "line": 200
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_zhuo_fu_ren",
    "speaker_name": "卓夫人",
    "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "text": "我们至少知道一个。",
    "tone": "平静",
    "chapter": 22,
    "line": 202
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
    "listener": "char_zhuo_fu_ren",
    "text": "谁？",
    "tone": "疑问",
    "chapter": 22,
    "line": 204
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_zhuo_fu_ren",
    "speaker_name": "卓夫人",
    "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "text": "你自己。",
    "tone": "平静",
    "chapter": 22,
    "line": 206
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_gong_zi_yu",
    "speaker_name": "公子羽",
    "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "text": "所以你现在总该已明白，你能活着到这里来，决不是运气。",
    "tone": "认真",
    "chapter": 22,
    "line": 214
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
    "listener": "char_gong_zi_yu",
    "text": "你这么样做，只因为你一定要证明你比我强？",
    "tone": "疑问",
    "chapter": 22,
    "line": 216
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_gong_zi_yu",
    "speaker_name": "公子羽",
    "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "text": "不错。",
    "tone": "平静",
    "chapter": 22,
    "line": 218
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_gong_zi_yu",
    "speaker_name": "公子羽",
    "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "text": "因为这一切都只有最强的人才能享受，你若能胜了我，这一切都是你的。",
    "tone": "悲哀",
    "chapter": 22,
    "line": 220
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
    "listener": "char_gong_zi_yu",
    "text": "这—切？",
    "tone": "疑问",
    "chapter": 22,
    "line": 222
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_zhuo_fu_ren",
    "speaker_name": "卓夫人",
    "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "text": "这一切的意思，就是所有的一切，其中不但包括了所有的财富、荣誉和权力，甚至还包括了我。",
    "tone": "微笑",
    "chapter": 22,
    "line": 224
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_zhuo_fu_ren",
    "speaker_name": "卓夫人",
    "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "text": "只要你能胜了他，连我都是你的。",
    "tone": "温柔",
    "chapter": 22,
    "line": 226
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_gong_zi_yu",
    "speaker_name": "公子羽",
    "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "text": "请，请随我来。",
    "tone": "平静",
    "chapter": 22,
    "line": 232
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_gong_zi_yu",
    "speaker_name": "公子羽",
    "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "text": "这就是我们的决斗之处。",
    "tone": "平静",
    "chapter": 22,
    "line": 238
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
    "listener": "char_gong_zi_yu",
    "text": "很好。",
    "tone": "平静",
    "chapter": 22,
    "line": 240
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_gong_zi_yu",
    "speaker_name": "公子羽",
    "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "text": "我们交手时，只能让六个人来观战，他们也就是这一场决斗的证人，你可以任意选择出三位。",
    "tone": "平静",
    "chapter": 22,
    "line": 250
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
    "listener": "char_gong_zi_yu",
    "text": "不必。",
    "tone": "冷酷",
    "chapter": 22,
    "line": 252
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_gong_zi_yu",
    "speaker_name": "公子羽",
    "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "text": "高手相争，胜负的关键往往会决定在一件很小的事上。有自己的朋友在旁边照顾，总比较安心些，你为什么要放弃这权利？",
    "tone": "认真",
    "chapter": 22,
    "line": 254
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
    "listener": "char_gong_zi_yu",
    "text": "因为我没有朋友。",
    "tone": "冷酷",
    "chapter": 22,
    "line": 256
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_gong_zi_yu",
    "speaker_name": "公子羽",
    "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "text": "这权利你还是不妨保留。我找来的人之中，如果有让你觉得不安的，你随时都可以拒绝。",
    "tone": "认真",
    "chapter": 22,
    "line": 258
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
    "listener": "char_gong_zi_yu",
    "text": "很好。",
    "tone": "平静",
    "chapter": 22,
    "line": 260
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_gong_zi_yu",
    "speaker_name": "公子羽",
    "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "text": "你连日劳累，精神体力都难免差些，不妨先在这里休养一段时候，所以决斗的日期，也由你来选择！",
    "tone": "认真",
    "chapter": 22,
    "line": 262
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
    "listener": "char_gong_zi_yu",
    "text": "明日此刻如何？",
    "tone": "认真",
    "chapter": 22,
    "line": 264
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_gong_zi_yu",
    "speaker_name": "公子羽",
    "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "text": "很好。",
    "tone": "平静",
    "chapter": 22,
    "line": 266
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
    "listener": "char_gong_zi_yu",
    "text": "那么明天我再来。",
    "tone": "平静",
    "chapter": 22,
    "line": 268
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_gong_zi_yu",
    "speaker_name": "公子羽",
    "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "text": "你不必走，我已经在这里为你准备了居室衣服，你可以安心休养，绝不会有人打扰你，你若有什么需要，我们也可以负责替你办到。",
    "tone": "认真",
    "chapter": 22,
    "line": 270
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
    "listener": "char_gong_zi_yu",
    "text": "看来这的确好像是场很公平的决斗。",
    "tone": "冷酷",
    "chapter": 22,
    "line": 272
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_gong_zi_yu",
    "speaker_name": "公子羽",
    "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "text": "绝对是的。",
    "tone": "平静",
    "chapter": 22,
    "line": 274
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
    "listener": "char_gong_zi_yu",
    "text": "我的棺材想必你也早已准备好了。",
    "tone": "冷酷",
    "chapter": 22,
    "line": 276
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_gong_zi_yu",
    "speaker_name": "公子羽",
    "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "text": "那是口上好的楠木棺材，是特地从柳州运来的，你若想先去看看，我也可以带你去。",
    "tone": "平静",
    "chapter": 22,
    "line": 278
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
    "listener": "char_gong_zi_yu",
    "text": "你已看过？",
    "tone": "疑问",
    "chapter": 22,
    "line": 280
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_gong_zi_yu",
    "speaker_name": "公子羽",
    "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "text": "我看过。",
    "tone": "平静",
    "chapter": 22,
    "line": 282
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
    "listener": "char_gong_zi_yu",
    "text": "你很满意。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 22,
    "line": 284
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_gong_zi_yu",
    "speaker_name": "公子羽",
    "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "text": "很满意。",
    "tone": "平静",
    "chapter": 22,
    "line": 286
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
    "listener": "char_gong_zi_yu",
    "text": "那就够了。",
    "tone": "冷酷",
    "chapter": 22,
    "line": 288
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_gong_zi_yu",
    "speaker_name": "公子羽",
    "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "text": "现在你也许只想去看看你的床。",
    "tone": "平静",
    "chapter": 22,
    "line": 290
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
    "listener": "char_gong_zi_yu",
    "text": "是的。",
    "tone": "平静",
    "chapter": 22,
    "line": 292
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_zhuo_fu_ren",
    "speaker_name": "卓夫人",
    "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "text": "又是一天过去了，日复一日，年复一年，这样的日子要过到什么时候为止？",
    "tone": "厌倦",
    "chapter": 22,
    "line": 302
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_zhuo_fu_ren",
    "speaker_name": "卓夫人",
    "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "text": "也许你认为我根本不该来的，我毕竟还是他的妻子，可是这种日子我实在已过得腻了，所以……",
    "tone": "无奈",
    "chapter": 22,
    "line": 310
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
    "listener": "char_zhuo_fu_ren",
    "text": "所以你希望我能击败他？",
    "tone": "疑问",
    "chapter": 22,
    "line": 312
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_zhuo_fu_ren",
    "speaker_name": "卓夫人",
    "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "text": "不错，我的确希望你能击败他，这么多年来，你是唯一有机会能击败他的一个人，你击败他之后，我的生活才会改变。",
    "tone": "认真",
    "chapter": 22,
    "line": 314
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
    "listener": "char_zhuo_fu_ren",
    "text": "胜者就能得到一切？",
    "tone": "疑问",
    "chapter": 22,
    "line": 316
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_zhuo_fu_ren",
    "speaker_name": "卓夫人",
    "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "text": "所有的一切。",
    "tone": "平静",
    "chapter": 22,
    "line": 318
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
    "listener": "char_zhuo_fu_ren",
    "text": "甚至连他的妻子也不例外？",
    "tone": "疑问",
    "chapter": 22,
    "line": 320
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_zhuo_fu_ren",
    "speaker_name": "卓夫人",
    "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "text": "是的。",
    "tone": "平静",
    "chapter": 22,
    "line": 322
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
    "listener": "char_zhuo_fu_ren",
    "text": "你既然不是个好妻子，他也不必冒这种险的。",
    "tone": "冷笑",
    "chapter": 22,
    "line": 324
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_zhuo_fu_ren",
    "speaker_name": "卓夫人",
    "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "text": "可是他要证明他比你强。",
    "tone": "认真",
    "chapter": 22,
    "line": 326
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
    "listener": "char_zhuo_fu_ren",
    "text": "证明给谁看？这里难道另外还有个主宰他命运的人？他这样做，也因为他根本没有选择的余地？",
    "tone": "冷酷",
    "chapter": 22,
    "line": 328
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_zhuo_fu_ren",
    "speaker_name": "卓夫人",
    "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "text": "你怎么会有这种想法的？",
    "tone": "惊讶",
    "chapter": 22,
    "line": 330
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
    "listener": "char_zhuo_fu_ren",
    "text": "你若是我，你会怎么想？",
    "tone": "冷酷",
    "chapter": 22,
    "line": 332
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_zhuo_fu_ren",
    "speaker_name": "卓夫人",
    "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "text": "我至少不会像你这样胡思乱想，我会一心想着要怎么样才能击败他。",
    "tone": "认真",
    "chapter": 22,
    "line": 334
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_zhuo_fu_ren",
    "speaker_name": "卓夫人",
    "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "text": "我虽然不能算是个好妻子，却是个很好的女人，你也应该看得出的。",
    "tone": "温柔",
    "chapter": 22,
    "line": 336
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
    "listener": "char_zhuo_fu_ren",
    "text": "我看不出。",
    "tone": "冷酷",
    "chapter": 22,
    "line": 338
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_zhuo_fu_ren",
    "speaker_name": "卓夫人",
    "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "text": "现在你不妨再看看。",
    "tone": "温柔",
    "chapter": 22,
    "line": 340
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_zhuo_fu_ren",
    "speaker_name": "卓夫人",
    "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "text": "只要你能战胜，这一切都是你的，但现在却还不是。",
    "tone": "温柔",
    "chapter": 22,
    "line": 348
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_zhuo_fu_ren",
    "speaker_name": "卓夫人",
    "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "text": "现在我还不是你的，可是你若需要，我可以找别人来陪你。",
    "tone": "调侃",
    "chapter": 22,
    "line": 356
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
    "listener": "char_zhuo_fu_ren",
    "text": "卓玉贞是不是在这里？",
    "tone": "焦急",
    "chapter": 22,
    "line": 360
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
    "listener": "char_zhuo_fu_ren",
    "text": "去找她来，立刻就来。",
    "tone": "焦急",
    "chapter": 22,
    "line": 364
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_zhuo_fu_ren",
    "speaker_name": "卓夫人",
    "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "text": "你为什么一定要选她？你为什么不选明月心？",
    "tone": "诡秘",
    "chapter": 22,
    "line": 370
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
    "listener": "char_zhuo_fu_ren",
    "text": "我……",
    "tone": "痛苦",
    "chapter": 22,
    "line": 376
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_zhuo_fu_ren",
    "speaker_name": "卓夫人",
    "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "text": "她也在这里，要不要我去带她来？",
    "tone": "悠然",
    "chapter": 22,
    "line": 378
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_zhuo_fu_ren",
    "speaker_name": "卓夫人",
    "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "text": "我知道你不会要的，你要的是卓玉贞，你喜欢的一向都是她那种低贱毒辣的女人。",
    "tone": "愤怒",
    "chapter": 22,
    "line": 380
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_zhuo_yu_zhen",
    "speaker_name": "卓玉贞",
    "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "text": "是你找我来的？",
    "tone": "冷酷",
    "chapter": 22,
    "line": 412
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
    "listener": "char_zhuo_yu_zhen",
    "text": "我找你来，只因为我本来有几件事要问你。",
    "tone": "平静",
    "chapter": 22,
    "line": 418
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_zhuo_yu_zhen",
    "speaker_name": "卓玉贞",
    "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "text": "现在呢？",
    "tone": "疑问",
    "chapter": 22,
    "line": 420
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
    "listener": "char_zhuo_yu_zhen",
    "text": "现在我已不想问，所以你不妨走。",
    "tone": "平静",
    "chapter": 22,
    "line": 422
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_zhuo_yu_zhen",
    "speaker_name": "卓玉贞",
    "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "text": "找我来报仇？",
    "tone": "冷酷",
    "chapter": 22,
    "line": 416
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_zhuo_yu_zhen",
    "speaker_name": "卓玉贞",
    "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "text": "你不想报复？",
    "tone": "疑问",
    "chapter": 22,
    "line": 424
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
    "listener": "char_zhuo_yu_zhen",
    "text": "不想。",
    "tone": "平静",
    "chapter": 22,
    "line": 426
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_zhuo_yu_zhen",
    "speaker_name": "卓玉贞",
    "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "text": "你也不想要我上床？",
    "tone": "冷酷",
    "chapter": 22,
    "line": 428
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_zhuo_yu_zhen",
    "speaker_name": "卓玉贞",
    "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "text": "你既然根本没有把我放在心上，又何必一定要我来？",
    "tone": "悲伤",
    "chapter": 22,
    "line": 440
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
    "listener": "char_zhuo_yu_zhen",
    "text": "就算我不该叫你来的，现在你还是一样可以走。",
    "tone": "平静",
    "chapter": 22,
    "line": 442
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_zhuo_yu_zhen",
    "speaker_name": "卓玉贞",
    "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "text": "不一样了。",
    "tone": "悲伤",
    "chapter": 22,
    "line": 444
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
    "listener": "char_zhuo_yu_zhen",
    "text": "有什么不一样？",
    "tone": "疑问",
    "chapter": 22,
    "line": 446
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_zhuo_yu_zhen",
    "speaker_name": "卓玉贞",
    "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "text": "不一样了，不一样了……",
    "tone": "悲伤",
    "chapter": 22,
    "line": 448
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_zhuo_yu_zhen",
    "speaker_name": "卓玉贞",
    "listener": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "text": "现在你总该已明白，为什么不一样了……",
    "tone": "痛苦",
    "chapter": 22,
    "line": 458
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_fu_hong_xue",
    "speaker_name": "傅红雪",
    "listener": "char_zhuo_yu_zhen",
    "text": "就因为我要你来，她就将你折磨成这样子？",
    "tone": "愤怒",
    "chapter": 22,
